  stimulus_text = 'The author suggests that the modern-day understanding of the concept of "wilderness" has shifted from a focus on the idea of untouched nature to a focus on a more human-centric notion of wilderness. For example, the author notes that some people use the term "wilderness" to refer to areas that have been shaped by human activity, such as areas with logging roads or farming land. Which of the following best describes the author’s view of "wilderness"?',
